<HEADLINE>
<P>
TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"I have a feeling that some people who are pushing these laws are thinking more 
like Communists and liberals." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Tony Acuerdo, one of seven members of the National Rifle Assn. from Los 
Angeles and Stockton who said they would file a lawsuit today asking the 
California Supreme Court to block ordinances that ban the sale and ownership of 
assault-type weapons. 
</P>
</TEXT>
