30-YEAR-OLD SLAIN IN GLENDALE SHOOTING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A30-year-old man was shot and killed Tuesday afternoon in a busy commercial 
area of Glendale, police said. 
</P>
<P>
Police responding to a report of shots being fired about 3:20 p.m. found the 
victim in the 1000 block of North Pacific Avenue, said Glendale Police Sgt. 
