AUTOMOBILE INDUSTRY -- UNITED STATES; AUTOMOBILE INDUSTRY -- JAPAN; BALANCE OF 
TRADE; SPARE PARTS; CHRYSLER CORP; IACOCCA, LEE 
</P>
